  "remarks": "\nAliaksandr Shepeleu is Head of the Department for Safety and Security of the Ministry of Internal Affairs. In his role as Head of the Department for Safety and Security, he is responsible for the actions of the Public Security Police and therefore bears responsibility for the serious human rights violations that were carried out following the election of 9 August, including torture or cruel, inhuman or degrading treatment or punishment.",
